    &lt;div class="blog-category"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.womenshealth.gov/blog/category/healthcare-and-women-0" hreflang="en"&gt; Healthcare and Women&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="blog-category"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.womenshealth.gov/blog/category/hiv-and-aids" hreflang="en"&gt; HIV and AIDS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="blog-category"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.womenshealth.gov/blog/category/reproductive-and-sexual-health" hreflang="en"&gt; Reproductive and Sexual Health&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="blog-category"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.womenshealth.gov/blog/category/violence-against-women" hreflang="en"&gt; Violence Against Women&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description>
  <pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2015 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
