    &lt;div class="blog-category"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.womenshealth.gov/blog/category/hiv-and-aids" hreflang="en"&gt; HIV and AIDS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="blog-category"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.womenshealth.gov/blog/category/violence-against-women" hreflang="en"&gt; Violence Against Women&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description>
